  }, 0);
  const groupTotal = fmt(sellPerPax * paxNum);
  const expList = selProds.map(p=>`- ${p.n} (${p.dl}): ${p.desc}`).join('\n');

  const sysRules = getAISystemRules();
  let prompt = '';
  if (type==='proposal') {
    prompt = sysRules + `You are the luxury travel writer for The Ant Adventures, a boutique Vietnam inbound tour company (brand color #2E7D52, voice: boutique, considered, locally rooted, quietly luxurious, never flashy).

Write a professional, evocative client-ready tour proposal summary.

CLIENT: ${custName} · ${pax} pax · ${style} style · ${tier} hotel tier
TRAVEL MONTH: ${month} 2026 · GUIDE LANGUAGE: ${lang}
SPECIAL REQUESTS: ${special}
TOTAL DURATION: ${totalD} days · SELL PRICE: $${fmt(sellPerPax)}/pax · GROUP TOTAL: $${groupTotal}

SELECTED EXPERIENCES:
${expList}

Write in The Ant Adventures luxury voice (second-person "you", sensory, unhurried). Structure:

